  "detailed_description": "<strong>Control the falling blocks, stack them correctly, and clear lines by filling them.</strong><br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each type of block has unique feature, using each feature appropriately is the key to success.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/31ab24eaa86da143806bbdc5dd017ec6.avif?t=1701885552\" width=525 height=70 /></span><br></li><li>Burn everything with flames! Always make sure the blocks are placed properly to avoid destroying everything with flames! Or burn them all!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/abcad05bd9373e2d31cf8048cabefdb8.poster.avif?t=1701885552\" width=294 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/abcad05bd9373e2d31cf8048cabefdb8.webm?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/abcad05bd9373e2d31cf8048cabefdb8.mp4?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Explosion is an art! Use bombs to save the situation from failure!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/4757b84f01d86d8b50521c4c08428263.poster.avif?t=1701885552\" width=702 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/4757b84f01d86d8b50521c4c08428263.webm?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/4757b84f01d86d8b50521c4c08428263.mp4?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>When you level up, more blocks will be unlocked.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/1178b5f5092a1a95d6b10091c97f95ea.avif?t=1701885552\" width=525 height=89 /></span></li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Place blocks to collect energy. Each time you fill up your energy, you can exchange it for a powerful bomb!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/f6735b3d1833982173516b5007efea20.poster.avif?t=1701885552\" width=620 height=606 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/f6735b3d1833982173516b5007efea20.webm?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/f6735b3d1833982173516b5007efea20.mp4?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Clear lines and level up. With each level up, the challenge increases in difficulty!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/8b72f9d639723642c77f0eb280509ef1.poster.avif?t=1701885552\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/8b72f9d639723642c77f0eb280509ef1.webm?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678760/extras/8b72f9d639723642c77f0eb280509ef1.mp4?t=1701885552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
